<script setup lang="ts">import type { BpmPolicySimulationResult,BpmPolicyVisualDraft } from '#/api/system/bpm/policy'; import { ref } from 'vue'; import { ElButton,ElEmpty,ElFormItem,ElTag } from 'element-plus'; import BpmIdentityPicker from '#/components/bpm/identity/bpm-identity-picker.vue'; import { simulateBpmPolicy } from '#/api/system/bpm/policy'; const props=defineProps<{draft:BpmPolicyVisualDraft}>(); const starter=ref(); const result=ref<BpmPolicySimulationResult>(); const loading=ref(false); async function run(){if(!starter.value)return;loading.value=true;try{result.value=await simulateBpmPolicy({draft:props.draft,starterEmployeeId:starter.value.stableId});}finally{loading.value=false}}</script>
<template><ElFormItem label="模拟发起人"><BpmIdentityPicker v-model="starter" kind="EMPLOYEE"/></ElFormItem><ElButton :disabled="!starter" :loading="loading" @click="run">运行模拟</ElButton><div v-if="result" class="result"><ElTag v-for="member in result.resolvedMembers" :key="member.employeeId">{{ member.employeeName }}</ElTag><p v-for="finding in result.findings" :key="finding.code" class="error">{{ finding.message }}</p><ElEmpty v-if="!result.resolvedMembers.length&&!result.findings.length" description="没有候选人"/></div></template><style scoped>.result{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:8px;margin-top:12px}.error{color:var(--el-color-danger)}</style>
